review_blob: Magnificent when cold-chilled. Swedish ship tourists beer. Original, royal pilsener aroma. Very good head, then a bit less.
Unbelievable! Herb, strong. Bavaria brewers must be proud while brewing this excellent beer, they dont want to hide their 8,6% alcohol. Urban.
Unusual, but nice. Golden, a bit smokey head but swift finish. Cant get enough of it, amousing, good friend. Funny name.
Lots of foam. Slightly fruit taste with the finish, but still strong. Not too interesting, best thing is 8,5%...
One of the nicest italian beers. Good-looking, friendly, blonde. Holiday refresher. Excellent lager.
